# UI and UX Quality

- Target a clean, modern, professional SaaS/company look.
- Use mobile-first responsive layout.
- Maintain consistent spacing with Tailwind scale.
- Build clear typography hierarchy for headings, body, and supporting text.
- Keep strong visual hierarchy and clear content flow.
- Use proper alignment and avoid cluttered layouts.

# Interaction and Polish

- Add subtle hover effects for interactive elements.
- Use smooth transitions (for example `transition-all` with `duration-200`).
- Keep interaction feedback consistent and unobtrusive.

# Performance and SEO

- Use Next.js `Image` component for images where appropriate.
- Use semantic HTML structure.
- Keep pages SEO-friendly with proper headings, metadata, and clean URLs.
